QuestData.Title: Where's My Head?
QuestData.Description: He's here, $n! Captain Grunwald is a high-ranking Alliance officer from Northwatch Hold, no doubt here to coordinate an assault on Orgrimmar with his night elven allies. We have observed him entering the tower southwest of here. I want his head, $c. I want to send it back to Northwatch to drive a wedge between our enemies!$B$BI've sent a goblin assassin, Slinky Sharpshiv, to the tower but she hasn't returned. Go find her. And get me that head!
QuestData.LogDescription: You've been sent to meet with the goblin assassin Slinky Sharpshiv at the base of the northern tower of Talrendis Point.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Meet with the goblin assassin Slinky Sharpshiv at the base of the northern tower of Talrendis Point in Azshara.
QuestData.RewardText: You're just in time, $c. I'm about to launch a lightning-strike precision assassination. Let's see...$B$BExplosives? Check.$BPneumatic grapplestabber? Check.$BPortable parachute? Check.$BCrippling nerve toxin?$B$B<Sharpshiv licks one of her blades.>$B$BCheck. Let's do this thing.
